netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain

Class DomainNameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.DomainNameObject

  • public class DomainNameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A value object used within the Netistrar Domain Lifecycle API methods to capture all of the properties of a domain name including related Contacts and Nameservers objects.
